title: SPY Presents: Heads Or Tails? w/ Clay Marzo + The Flynn
description: Clay's surfing is raw, unscripted and exciting to watch. It's captive because you never know what he's going to do on a wave and it draws you in and puts you on the edge of your seat. It's a roller coaster ride on speed.
